{"tid":854920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這是一件離奇的車禍⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T01:20:04.000Z","uid":29269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1894b63a3e58bf912ced3ec18e78eac34cf1427f","tid":854920,"uid":29269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"轉發：這是一件離奇的車禍，在台灣高雄有一位騎機車的老先生被一輛穿越時空的車子撞倒。老先生發現對面根本就沒有路，全都是店鋪，而且也找不到這輛肇事的車，只有目擊者的行車記錄儀錄到一輛轎車以飛快的速度撞倒這一位老先生的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n今日收到呢段片，點睇都唔似剪接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/004610_0ed40ea92ffc53d8a63112c792edb864.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F004610_0ed40ea92ffc53d8a63112c792edb864.png&h=b1a426d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/004614_b31b3dfe709ea3965cde732b85ce25a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F004614_b31b3dfe709ea3965cde732b85ce25a2.png&h=86729a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/004618_16301f1cacd4b37f9e07f4c11bd06e86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F004618_16301f1cacd4b37f9e07f4c11bd06e86.png&h=11c748b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/004623_8fb0c363183c6636b74f5a46ff78e9bc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F004623_8fb0c363183c6636b74f5a46ff78e9bc.gif&h=ef4db973&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"151aaab959900d9b4637071197b30cf778995484","tid":854920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb085bfa200b9562a83a2de71631260450045ca","tid"